  "What is a token lock?": "什么是代币锁仓？",
  "A lock takes tokens out of circulation and hands control to an on-chain program instead of a wallet. The tokens can only be released on a fixed, public schedule — nobody, not even the team, can pull them early. It’s the difference between a promise and a padlock: anyone can verify it on-chain.": "锁仓将代币移出流通，并把控制权交给链上程序而非钱包。代币只能按照固定、公开的时间表释放——任何人，甚至团队，都无法提前取出。这就是承诺与挂锁的区别：任何人都能在链上验证。",
